name: The pride of Mr Lion V3

metadata.name: The pride of Mr Lion #1
metadata.description:
Based on the collectors and community resources gathered on the Orinft platform, we will launch the first NFT project: The pride of Mr Lion, which is a collection of digital collectibles consisting of 3,333 Mr Lion NFTs. It includes hundreds of attributes with different rarities, such as hats, eyes, demeanor, clothing, backgrounds, etc.
We programmatically generate 3333 unique Mr Lions by random combination, each with a different expression and dress. 
Each Mr Lion costs 0.5 ETH.
